01:15:15,305 --> 01:15:16,680
Hajde.

801
01:15:30,537 --> 01:15:32,392
Hvala ti.

802
01:15:39,112 --> 01:15:40,967
Ne mogu plakati.

803
01:15:44,328 --> 01:15:46,597
