za Donald.

804
01:15:48,872 --> 01:15:50,759
Ne mogu više plakati.

805
01:15:54,663 --> 01:15:56,801
ocu da pobegnem odavde.

806
01:15:59,111 --> 01:16:00,572
Ne bez tebe.

807
01:16:17,957 --> 01:16:19,812
Donecu ti.

808
01:16:36,997 --> 01:16:41,404
Ne bih te zamarala, John,
ali mislim da konacno imamo pauzu.

809
01:16:41,476 --> 01:16:44,476
