- Ne.

890
01:22:47,245 --> 01:22:49,700
- Da li znaš ime barmena?
- Sacekaj minut!

891
01:22:52,077 --> 01:22:55,011
Tommy, ako postoji rupa u
tvom secanju...

892
01:22:55,084 --> 01:22:58,826
ili ako postoji period u tvom
ivotu...

893
01:22:58,892 --> 01:23:01,096
kojeg se ne moeš setiti--

894
01:23:02,316 --> 01:23:04,771
ako postoji išta cega se
ne moeš setiti...

895
01:23:04,844 --> 01:23:08,673
veoma je vano da otkrijemo
zajedno...

896
01:23:08,748 --> 01:23:10,603
šta je to.

897
01:23:18,762 --> 01:23:21,991
Pokušavaš me baciti u
jebeni Bellevue.

898
01:23:27,306 --> 01:23:30,023
Šta se dodavola ovde dešava, John?
Jesi li ga uhapsio ili ne?

899
01:23:30,090 --> 01:23:33,865
Ne, Saly, nisam ga uhapsio. 
Vodi ga na pregled, molim te.

900
01:23:33,930 --> 01:23:35,686
Hajde. Idemo, Tommy.

901
01:23:35,754 --> 01:23:38,437
- Hajde.
- Radije bih u jebenu pecinu...

902
01:23:38,506 --> 01:23:40,361
nego u jebenu mentalnu kliniku.

903
01:23:40,426 --> 01:23:42,335
Bei odavde!

904
01:23:44,233 --> 01:23:46,088
Stani! Covek pobee!

905
01:23:47,177 --> 01:23:48,289
Nemoj! Saly!

906
01:23:50,825 --> 01:23:52,287
Potegnuo je no na mene!

907
01:23:57,064 --> 01:23:59,300
cekaj. Stani!

908
01:24:03,336 --> 01:24:05,310
Tommy, ne trci!

909
01:24:05,384 --> 01:24:06,911
Hajde. Idemo.

910
01:24:41,606 --> 01:24:44,027
Tommy, stani!

911
01:24:58,533 --> 01:24:59,481
Okreni se.

912
01:25:00,965 --> 01:25:02,110
Idi na 49-ti.

913
01:25:07,236 --> 01:25:08,446
Idi ispred njega.

914
01:25:13,796 --> 01:25:14,941
Stani!

915
01:25:24,387 --> 01:25:26,242
Hej, dobar posao.

916
01:25:27,683 --> 01:25:29,755
Nije cak ni znao
šta radi, Saly.

917
01:25:29,826 --> 01:25:32,477
- Sacuvala sam dravi 200,000.
- Zovi upravnika.

918
01:25:36,066 --> 01:25:37,179
Hej.

919
01:25:38,049 --> 01:25:39,904
Bolestan je, Saly.

920
01:25:44,385 --> 01:25:46,044
Bolestan!

921
01:25:49,025 --> 01:25:50,432
Da.

922
01:25:50,497 --> 01:25:53,148
Laura, imamo ga. Gotovo je.
Pakuj se.

923
01:25:54,273 --> 01:25:56,182
- Halo?
- Šta?

924
01:25:56,257 --> 01:25:59,290
Imamo ga. Gotovo je.
Pakuj se. Vodim te odavde.

925
01:25:59,361 --> 01:26:01,597
- U redu. U redu.
- Volim te.

926
01:26:04,544 --> 01:26:06,399
Volim te.

927
01:26:14,400 --> 01:26:18,360
Poslati smo kuci sad, Miss Mars.
Treba vam nešto pre nego odemo?

928
01:26:18,431 --> 01:26:20,471
Ne.

929
01:26:20,543 --> 01:26:22,430
- Hvala vam.
- Nema na cemu.

930
01:27:30,362 --> 01:27:32,217
Izvinite me.

931
01:28:13,720 --> 01:28:15,149
Ne!

932
01:28:40,822 --> 01:28:43,244
Ne!

933
01:28:43,318 --> 01:28:46,384
Bei! Bei!

934
01:29:15,636 --> 01:29:18,003
Ima li nekoga ovde?
Ko je tamo?

935
01:29:18,068 --> 01:29:20,719
Ne! Ne, Neville.
On je u liftu.

936
01:29:20,788 --> 01:29:23,788
-Videla sam da je ubio nekog u liftu.
-Nema nikoga u liftu.

937
01:29:25,203 --> 01:29:27,342
Nema nikoga u liftu.
Sad sam odande došao.

938
01:29:27,412 --> 01:29:29,932
- Videla sam--
- Gotovo je, veruj mi. Tommy je mrtav.

939
01:29:30,003 --> 01:29:33,264
Mrtav je. Tommy je mrtav.

940
01:29:33,331 --> 01:29:35,186
- Tommy je mrtav?
- Da.

941
01:29:37,330 --> 01:29:39,818
NE razumem.

942
01:29:39,891 --> 01:29:42,444
- Zašto bi ubio on sve te ljude?
- Mrzeo te je.

943
01:29:42,515 --> 01:29:45,329
- Mrzeo te je.
- Ne.

944
01:29:45,394 --> 01:29:47,369
- Imao je ideju--
- Nije mrzeo--

945
01:29:47,442 --> 01:29:49,351
Imao je ideju da...

946
01:29:49,426 --> 01:29:52,109
je tvoj rad izazivao nasilje.

947
01:29:52,178 --> 01:29:55,244
Imao je ideju da smrt ne bi
trebala biti korišcena...

948
01:29:55,313 --> 01:29:57,168
da se prodaju stvari.

949
01:29:58,546 --> 01:30:00,750
Smrt...

950
01:30:00,818 --> 01:30:02,760
je svet stvar.

951
01:30:04,081 --> 01:30:06,798
O cemu pricaš?

952
01:30:06,865 --> 01:30:09,799
Njegova majka.

953
01:30:09,872 --> 01:30:11,530
Ne razumem.

954
01:30:11,600 --> 01:30:13,771
Tommy-jeva majka.

955
01:30:13,841 --> 01:30:16,775
Histericna ena.
Bila je kurva, znaš?

956
01:30:16,848 --> 01:30:19,215
Ostavljala ga je da sedi 3,
4 dana...

957
01:30:19,280 --> 01:30:21,135
u maloj sobi--

958
01:30:24,367 --> 01:30:25,928
u sitim pelenama...

959
01:30:25,999 --> 01:30:28,072
dok je ona prodavala svoje
dupe gore i dole...

960
01:30:28,144 --> 01:30:30,599
ulicama glavnog grada.

961
01:30:30,672 --> 01:30:33,868
- Nije bilo lepo.
- Ne.

962
01:30:33,935 --> 01:30:36,717
Ne. To je Tommy-jeva prica.

963
01:30:36,783 --> 01:30:39,271
Onda jednog dana otac dolazi kuci.

964
01:30:41,231 --> 01:30:43,784
Mislim da je bio otac.

965
01:30:43,855 --> 01:30:45,709
Moda je bio John,
znaš. Trik.

966
01:30:45,775 --> 01:30:47,629
Bio je njegov otac.

967
01:30:49,390 --> 01:30:53,001
Uznemiren zbog stanja njegovog deteta,
prereza joj grkljan...

968
01:30:53,070 --> 01:30:55,590
pravo na mestu.

969
01:30:59,405 --> 01:31:01,827
Sedeo sam i gledao kako
joj krv kaplje...

970
01:31:03,214 --> 01:31:06,181
dok nije dobila boju
njene kose.

971
01:31:06,253 --> 01:31:08,107
Znaš?

972
01:31:11,853 --> 01:31:13,227
Neville, rekao si "Ja".

973
01:31:14,860 --> 01:31:17,762
Ne znam šta vidiš u tom
kuckinom sinu.

974
01:31:17,836 --> 01:31:20,902
Ne moe platiti ni racun. Iskljucili
su mu struju sinoc.

975
01:31:20,972 --> 01:31:24,900
Ne moe završiti disertaciju.
Radi na tome 3 godine.

976
01:31:24,972 --> 01:31:27,819
Znaš?
Ja sam ta koja ga dri u kondiciju.

977
01:31:27,883 --> 01:31:29,738
Vidiš ovo telo?
To je moj rad.

978
01:31:29,803 --> 01:31:32,291
Ako je do njega,
teila bih 98 funti.

979
01:31:32,364 --> 01:31:36,390
Ja sam ta koja ga hrani.
Ja placam racune.

980
01:31:36,460 --> 01:31:38,401
Ja odgovaram an kartice.

981
01:31:41,770 --> 01:31:44,039
Ja sam ta koju eliš.

982
01:32:27,016 --> 01:32:28,871
Volim te!

983
01:33:42,371 --> 01:33:44,891
Ako me voliš...

984
01:33:44,963 --> 01:33:47,134
ubij ga.

985
01:33:49,794 --> 01:33:50,590
Sad.

986
01:33:52,867 --> 01:33:54,176
Molim te.

987
01:33:54,242 --> 01:33:56,663
Molim te ubij.

988
01:33:58,434 --> 01:34:01,052
Ako me voliš, ubiceš ga.

989
01:34:01,122 --> 01:34:02,714
Ne.

990
01:34:06,689 --> 01:34:08,544
Volim te.

991
01:34:15,521 --> 01:34:18,139
Molim te ubij ga.

992
01:34:40,927 --> 01:34:45,269
Policijski operator 834.
Gde je urba?

993
01:34:45,343 --> 01:34:47,383
elim da prijavim smrt.

994
01:34:47,455 --> 01:34:50,651
Molim vas dajte mi vaše
ime i adresu.

995
01:34:53,343 --> 01:34:56,026
Dajte mi adresu, molim vas.

996
01:34:56,094 --> 01:34:58,363
Došao je ovde da me ubije.

997
01:34:58,430 --> 01:35:02,172
Smirite se. Neko ce doci
za par trenutaka.

998
01:35:02,238 --> 01:35:04,922
Nije to mogao...

999
01:35:04,990 --> 01:35:09,594
- Gospodo?
- Zato što--

1000
01:35:09,662 --> 01:35:12,117
Madam, da bih vam pomogla,
moram znati vaše ime...

1001
01:35:12,190 --> 01:35:14,044
i vašu adresu.

1002
01:35:14,110 --> 01:35:17,590
Stvarno me je voleo.

1003
01:35:20,796 --> 01:35:23,317
Samo mi dajte vaše ime.

1004
01:35:23,389 --> 01:35:25,363
Šta?

1005
01:35:25,436 --> 01:35:27,291
Vaše ime.

1006
01:35:37,500 --> 01:35:39,355
Ja sam Laura Mars.

